NO. 2018-OB-1935 Supreme Court of Louisiana. January 14, 2019

IN RE: Appeal of the DECISION OF the DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL NO. 2018-INT-1244

Granted for the sole purpose of transferring the matter to the Office of the Disciplinary Counsel for review by the Chief Disciplinary Counsel, See Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 11(A).
